From 58fc8ebc79530ffac96208843cccf6a2abe1b2e5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 8 Jul 2025 16:54:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: wifi: ath12k: DP: Add support for telemetry
 interactions with driver

Add support to
	- Register and de-register telemetry peer context during
MSDUQ allocation and link peer deletion respectively.
	- Update service classes to the telemetry driver when
configured and disabled.
	- Update selected SDWF statistics to the telemetry driver.
	- Send the requested statistics to the telemetry driver.
	- Clear accumulated statistics in the telemetry driver
via vendor interface.
	- Notify userspace via vendor interface upon breach
detection from the telemetry driver.

Following patch changes are also present
	- 784-06-ath12k-sawf-Add-telemetry-agent-interface-and-config.patch

Signed-off-by: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
